videos.description: Adrio Bailey attempts to take a shot but is met with a block from Grant Williams.
videos.headline: Williams blocks early for Tennessee

videos.description: Admiral Schofield kicks it out to an open Jordan Bone who drills a 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Tennessee's Bone drains trey

videos.description: Jordan Bone forces the steal and takes it all the way home for a two-handed flush.
videos.headline: Tennessee's Bone goes coast-to-coast

videos.description: Anton Beard is fouled on his way to the rim and gets the unlikely basket to fall in.
videos.headline: Arkansas' Beard makes diving and-1

videos.description: Jordan Bone leads the way with 19 points as the Volunteers knock off the Razorbacks 84-66 to reach the SEC tournament finals where they will face Kentucky.
videos.headline: Tennessee rolls past Arkansas to the finals
